OL,3,CThe Somerset farmers fighting for a
OL,4,CBritish wool revival
OL,6,FSomerset farmers say consumers need to
OL,7,Finvest in quality products for the
OL,8,FBritish wool industry to survive.
OL,10,FAs the weather gets warmer, sheep
OL,11,Ffarmers are turning their attention to
OL,12,Fshearing.
OL,14,FWool may be a by-product of sheep
OL,15,Ffarming but it is definitely not an
OL,16,Feasy source of extra income.
OL,18,FIt is a physically demanding job but
OL,19,Fthat does not means there are great
OL,20,Frewards.
