OL,3,CThe Somerset farmers fighting for a
OL,4,CBritish wool revival
OL,6,FAll of this raises questions over the
OL,7,Ffuture of the British wool industry.
OL,9,FAndy farms in the Mendip Hills and has
OL,10,Fbeen shearing all around the world.
OL,11,FOver the years, there has been a lot
OL,12,Fof change in the industry.
OL,14,FAndy said: "With the wool industry...
OL,15,FI guess it's in a bit of a despondent
OL,16,Fmood. Farmers aren't getting that much
OL,17,Fmoney for their wool."
OL,19,FRecently, cheap imports and fast
OL,20,Ffashion have brought about a decline
OL,21,Fin the British wool industry
