OL,3,CThe Somerset farmers fighting for a
OL,4,CBritish wool revival
OL,6,F"There's more work to be done, but I
OL,7,Fcan see that the momentum is starting
OL,8,Fto shift. And for the longer term that
OL,9,Fmakes me feel a lot more positive and
OL,10,FI do believe there's a future for wool.
OL,12,FAndy said: "For the wool industry to
OL,13,Fdo well, and I think it needs to be
OL,14,Flooked at globally, we need the
OL,15,Fconsumers to support us.
OL,17,F"We need big businesses who are
OL,18,Finvolved with the wool industry to
OL,19,Fstand up and state the case that
OL,20,Fnatural fibres are much better than
OL,21,Fsynthetics."
