OL,3,CThe Somerset farmers fighting for a
OL,4,CBritish wool revival
OL,6,FAndy's wife Jen Hunter makes products
OL,7,Ffrom their wool, to sell to a wider
OL,8,Fmarket.
OL,10,FJen said: "We wanted to be price
OL,11,Fmakers, rather than price takers back
OL,12,Fin 2008.
OL,14,F"Andrew and myself really like to wear
OL,15,Fwool. To be able to sell your own
OL,16,Fproducts to a final consumer and they
OL,17,Fcan feel the love you have for the
OL,18,Fsheep, and they take that with them,
OL,19,Fand they give the fleece a new life,
OL,20,Fit's really special."
