OL,4,CBritish wool revival
OL,6,FJen and Andy are now looking towards
OL,7,Fthe future but training the future
OL,8,Fgeneration.
OL,10,FNancy Housego is studying textiles
OL,11,Fdesign at Central St Martin's in
OL,12,FLondon. She specialises in knitwear
OL,13,Fand wanted to focus on where her
OL,14,Fsupplies were coming from.
OL,16,FNancy said: "Before I came here, I was
OL,17,Factually working at a fast fashion
OL,18,Fbrand in London that was specialising
OL,19,Fin knitwear, so it's very different.
